description:
This is going up as a bonus for the month of May. We had this match ready to go up for season 11 however with Audrey's recent announcement of retirement from wrestling we are putting it up as a bonus. She will not be continuing in the FW tournament and we are sad to see her go and we sure are happy to give this shoot to the members as a bonus.
Nikki "Tricky" Darling just hasn't had any luck on our mats. We've only put her against feather weights but that hasn't helped her case any. She's still learning the ropes and still getting the fist of fury when she fails.
Audrey Rose is back for another great performance. She has an answer for anything the rookie throws at her. She shows us why she was ranked as one of our best feather weights for season 10. fisting 69 in round 4 both the winner and the loser get fisted. The winner wants to show up the loser one more time by beating her at a fisting competition. They both turn up winners when they both cum hard
title: Nikki Darling vs. Audrey Rose in a super sexy feather weight BONUS!
